.TH "lpfc_set_rport_loss_tmo" 9 "lpfc_set_rport_loss_tmo" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
lpfc_set_rport_loss_tmo \- Set the rport dev loss tmo
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" lpfc_set_rport_loss_tmo
.BI "(struct fc_rport *rport "  ","
.BI "uint32_t timeout "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "rport" 12
fc rport address.
.IP "timeout" 12
new value for dev loss tmo.
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
If timeout is non zero set the dev_loss_tmo to timeout, else set
dev_loss_tmo to one.
